{
  "title": "Dreamy Tunisian Pea Eggplant Tagine",
  "description": "A pungent and pillowy Tunisian dish featuring pea and eggplant, perfect for a hangover cure, made with beurre monte and nut free friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
